            <title><![CDATA[being mindful]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<article><h1>being mindful</h1><p>“I took the
dog for a walk not knowing where I was going…I just walked. I had never just
wandered out without a plan before…with my anxiety I always needed to know
where I was going. It was a totally new experience and it was fine…I felt happy
and elated…I realised it was perfectly OK to be without knowing.”</p><img src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/the-grid-img/p/5f633ce95e3fad0401cf3566f62a477f81adba16.jpg"></article>]]></description>
